* Michael Brecker, musician
* Laurentino Cortizo, the President of Panama
* Pat Hingle, actor
* Paul Motian, musician
* Amrish Puri, actor
* Carl Sagan, astrophysicist
* Susan Sontag, author
* Norm Macdonald, comedian

