<doc id="186414" wikidata="Q28730846" url="?curid=186414" title="Ethnic groups in Gabon">
<text>Despite Gabon&#x27;s small population (just over a million), this Central African country is home to many different Bantu tribes and a small pygmy population.

Here is a partial list of the ethnic groups in Gabon, by province.

